com.batchfrommars.component

Class ComponentII

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • com.batchfrommars.component.ComponentII
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BatchComponentII, CompareComponent, MergeSortComponent, MultiMergeSortComponent, SortComponent

    public abstract class ComponentII
extends java.lang.Thread
    ComponentII is parent class of every components in BatchFromMars. Every component has inputFileList, outputFileList and lastComponentList. ComponentII provide some method to access these member.Extend ComponentII and implement act method, then you can create a component in BatchFromMars system.
    Author:
    JohnFromMars
